race.comment: PEARLER (10) has returned in strong order this campaign, knocking her maiden off third-up and making it back-to-back wins at Orange. Gave another bold sight last time at Moruya, only to be reeled in late. Backs up quickly and only needs to hold her form to be featuring heavily again. ROYALIFY (3) was a determined winner fresh and followed it up with a solid chasing effort at Orange last time. Peaking now and has enough pace to offset his wide alley and give a bold sight. GEOSTORM (13) is knocking on the door and is busting to break through. Backs up quickly and doesn't need to improve much to get his just deserts. Last start winner DRUNKEN SAILOR (1) also holds claims and is worth some thought.
